1.en: I then unfolded the note and spread it out in front of me.
1.cn: 我展开短信，将其摊在我面前。

2.en: V- shaped bar bent to a half- circle is attached to the body , close to the front of the disc in full open position .
2.cn: 一个V形杆弯曲成半圆状附加在阀体上，在阀门处于全开状态时紧靠阀瓣前部。

3.en: Owing to this point, study on the effectiveness of interest rate policy has been taken as a front-line subject of theoretical research.
3.cn: 利率政策日益成为主要的宏观经济政策之一，对于利率政策的研究也成为经济领域的前沿课题之一。

0.en: Can I sit at the front too? And me, me. Oh, I'm sorry children. You can't all sit at the front. Oh.
0.cn: 我也可以坐到前面去吗？我也要。对不起啦，孩子们，你们不可以一起和我都坐在前面。

1.en: Madam Gazelle. I feel a bit sick, can I go to the front, please? Ok, Pedro, you can go to the front of the train.
1.cn: 加塞利老师，我有点恶心。请问我可以坐到前面去吗？可以，佩德罗，你可以去火车的前面。

2.en: Madam Gazelle. I feel a bit sick, can I go to the front, please? Okay, Pedro, you can go to the front of the train.
2.cn: 羚羊夫人，我感觉有点不舒服，我可以坐到前面去吗？好的，佩德罗，那么你就做到前面去吧。

3.en: You want to sit front or back? I'll sit over there.
3.cn: 你想坐前面还是后面？我就坐那里吧。

4.en: After dinner, me, her, and Pepper all fell asleep in front of the fire.
4.cn: 晚饭后，我们两个和辣椒，在炉火前面睡着了。

5.en: Bunking will be arranged with youngest at the front and veterans at the back.
5.cn: 床铺按照年龄顺序，年轻的在前面，老兵在后面。

6.en: Yeah, but no backside. And a front side that shouldn't be allowed outside.
6.cn: 是啊，但没有后面[屁股] ，而"前面"根本不能掏出外面见人。

7.en: Okay, darlings. If everyone will focus their attention to the front of the room, war.
7.cn: 好了，亲爱的。请大家把注意力集中到教室前面的黑板上，战争。

8.en: Well, who you gonna hit on? The girl in front of us got strawberry. That's your favorite.
8.cn: 你准备搭讪哪个？排我们前面的那个姑娘买了草莓味，你的最爱。

9.en: It's the equivalent of crashing at 94 miles per hour into a wall with a door in front of it.
9.cn: 这相当于以94英里每小时的速度顶着它前面的一扇门撞进墙里。

10.en: Okay? Yeah, it's a perfectly good word. I mean, you put it in front of dokay And you really got something.
10.cn: 还行？这个词很好啊，放在“不错”前面，效果也很好啊。

11.en: You want to take the front of the ship off? Sure. The nose airlock alone is 400 kg.
11.cn: 你想把整个飞行器的前面都拆了？没错，顶部的气密舱有400公斤重呢。

12.en: Or'd got hit in the back. It blew most of his guts and intestines out his front off for everywhere.
12.cn: 若是击中背部，把他的大部分内脏跟肠子从前面炸出落得到处都是。

13.en: I just hope that when Hal get shot it's through the front of his jacket. Like a simple entry wound not what you miss.
13.cn: 我只希望哈尔中枪时，是穿过夹克前面。像个简单射伤，不足为虑。

14.en: It's pickup day. The cans are in front. I know. You need some help? No. Maybe I'll do it later.
14.cn: 今天是垃圾回收日，垃圾车就在前面。我知道，要我帮忙吗? 不用了，我还是过会儿再去吧。

15.en: Fine? You said it was fine? Yeah, it's a perfectly good word. You put it in front of wine or dining, and you've really got something.
15.cn: 挺好？你说挺好？这个词很好啊，放在“酒”和“餐”前面，效果不是很好嘛。

16.en: Okay, first question. Ah, right up front. Hi. Hi. Hi, I'm Alex. Long-time reader, first-time grabber.
16.cn: 好吧，第一个问题。前面这位。你好。你好。你好，我是艾丽克斯。长期粉丝，但第一次抓住机会。

17.en: Hey, kids. Come here. Do you see anything right here? Yeah. It looks like a boat. A boat. Yeah. Right in front of the Statue of Liberty.
17.cn: 嗨，小子。到这里来，你在这里看到什么了吗？看起来像一只船。一只船。正好在自由女神前面。

18.en: You see the disk in front and then when it goes around you see the disk wrap up around the top of the black hole and wrap around the bottom of the black hole.
18.cn: 你看到前面的吸积盘，然后当它绕着，你会看到吸积盘绕着黑洞顶部包裹，然后绕着黑洞底部弯曲。

19.en: What's that? It's our bicycle. I sit at the front and Mummy pig sit at the back. And we can put these two seats on the back for Peppa and George.
19.cn: 那是什么？这是我们的自行车。我坐在前面，猪妈妈就坐在我后面。我们还能把这两个位置放在后面给佩奇和乔治坐。
